short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: VAST browser extension for Google Calendar and Outlook

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The VAST browser extensions adds a VAST icon to your Google Calendar and Outlook Calendar event. This helps you seamlessly open events up in VAST if your accounts are integrated.
